This is the classic ASG magazine that was the real deal. It is extremely hard to find these issues, and the collection I have gathered here is definitely not complete, but it is absolutely everything I could find. Not much is out on the web about these issues...they kind of just went away and now if you want to but a hard copy, you're going to pay for it. Enjoy these mags, there is still a lot of really great info to be found here. Please seed and lemme know if there are more out there that I am missing. Thanks to all!
